{"tid":753783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係唔想旅行去做電燈膽","createTime":"2018-07-24T01:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T03:34:52.000Z","uid":146358,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"80f0bfce560f48020fecf92de4c4da0e8d391d37","tid":753783,"uid":146358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:48:29.000Z","msg":"我嚟緊12月尾同兩男兩女去旅行順手跨年<br />\n機票錢都俾咗<br />\n其中一pair係情侶<br />\n我一開始諗住唔緊要啦仲有個男仔陪我<br />\n點知去到今日就出事了<br />\n另外嗰一男一女好似就嚟拍拖<br />\n我完全唔想去到做電燈膽<br />\n自己又冇女<br />\n到底點搞好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續一齊去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔去啦仲去"},{"pid":"04dbafe1451c15c218121000217b95e244d44dca","tid":753783,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"（show block user 屌我啦屌我啦）"},{"pid":"b75eaaf2f0c721afb472ec4cdaf020064b54d4da","tid":753783,"uid":163207,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"搶先同個男仔一齊,等條女做電燈膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0366eebf8608ab74a655ef441ecc58ac74f21a","tid":753783,"uid":25935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"同一個女仔拍拖 即刻報埋佢個名"},{"pid":"2f8826863d77a4ed60680e475a03074343785208","tid":753783,"uid":53588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"揾多條女一齊去 到時book房 剩返你同條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8269425ecad1e02ba7f6144b4201c8917d68453b","tid":753783,"uid":50894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:52:11.000Z","msg":"去到做五星戰隊隊長"},{"pid":"23b00f89463a188c870c7941c18d9a4a0ba71e89","tid":753783,"uid":146358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8269425ecad1e02ba7f6144b4201c8917d68453b","tid":753783,"uid":50894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T01:52:1